<br>
For the past few months as my character Bagend ive done some pretty stupid things.  It got to the point where I couldnt even shout LFG.  Things like Ninja Looting a Pod of Seawater off a GM Event version of Faydeder in LOIO, and scamming people for MQ's.  <br>
<br>
I am posting this to say sorry to all the people that were harmed by me and my actions.  Yes I tried to start a new character and get a fresh start but people found out that I was also Bagend.  <br>
<br>
In conclusion, the character Bagend is no more and will never be seen again (he was deleted).  &quot;Lancerblood&quot; is my current main. My alts are as follows:<br>
<br>
Lvl 12 Monk - Ravenfists<br>
Lvl 19 Cleric - Latonia<br>
Lvl 18 Beastlord - Lancero<br>
Lvl 10 Paladin - Baliden<br>
<br>
Main Character: Lvl 49 Warrior - Lancerblood<br>
<br>
Im asking forgiveness from the RN community for my actions, I know it will take time to prove that I have changed but believe I will.  <br>
<br>
One last thing,  Anyone that I have scammed/harmed/ninja looted off please send me a tell in game or post on this topic and I will find some way to reimburse you.<br>
<br>
Thanks for hearing me out,<br>
<br>
 <p>Lancerblood
<BR>The Confused Warrior
